interface for detecting physiological indicators of anxiety in children.‚Äù <em>Frontiers in Neuroscience</em>. 10:401. <a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.3389/fnins.2016.00401">doi:10.3389/fnins.2016.00401</a>.</p>

